'''喬瑟夫·尼可拉斯·蓋洛'''（{{lang-en|Joseph Nicholas Gallo}}，{{bd|1993年|11月19日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，曾為[[一壘手|一壘手]]和[[三壘手|三壘手]]，目前效力於紐約洋基。蓋洛於2015年登上大聯盟，並在2019年入選明星賽。

==職業生涯==
===德州遊騎兵===
[[2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，遊騎兵在第一輪39順位選進蓋洛。<ref>{{cite web |author=RunThisTown (Matt Philips) |url=http://www.lasvegassun.com/news/2012/jun/04/bishop-gormans-joey-gallo-goes-39th-overall-texas-/ |title=Bishop Gorman's Joey Gallo goes 39th overall to the Texas Rangers |publisher=Lasvegassun.com |access-date=September 3, 2013 |archive-date=2018-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930120118/https://lasvegassun.com/news/2012/jun/04/bishop-gormans-joey-gallo-goes-39th-overall-texas-/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://texas.rangers.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120604&content_id=32759158&vkey=news_tex&c_id=tex |title=Rangers draft high school power on Day 1 |publisher=Texas.rangers.mlb.com |date=May 24, 2013 |access-date=September 3, 2013 |archive-date=2013-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110093319/http://texas.rangers.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120604&content_id=32759158&vkey=news_tex&c_id=tex |dead-url=no }}</ref>他以225萬美元成功加盟遊騎兵。<ref name=nola>{{cite web | url=http://www.nola.com/lsu/index.ssf/2015/06/joey_gallo_homers_debut_lsu.html | title=Former LSU signee Joey Gallo homers in major league debut | publisher=The Times-Picayune | date=June 2, 2015 | access-date=June 30, 2017 | author=Dabe, Christopher | archive-date=2018-09-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919211550/https://www.nola.com/lsu/index.ssf/2015/06/joey_gallo_homers_debut_lsu.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2015年====
6月1日，蓋洛進入球隊的40人名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasnews.com/sports/texas-rangers/headlines/20150601-grant-why-rangers-feel-time-is-right-for-joey-gallo-to-join-big-club.ece|title=Grant: Why Rangers feel time is right for Joey Gallo to join big club|work=dallasnews.com|access-date=June 2, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924131249/http://www.dallasnews.com/sports/texas-rangers/headlines/20150601-grant-why-rangers-feel-time-is-right-for-joey-gallo-to-join-big-club.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在隔天升上大聯盟，並在初登板敲出大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/128160738/joey-gallo-homers-in-second-big-league-at-bat|title=Gallo homers in second big league at-bat|access-date=June 2, 2015|last=Sullivan|first=T.R.|date=June 2, 2015|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071324/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/128160738/joey-gallo-homers-in-second-big-league-at-bat|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月5日，蓋洛單場吞下4次三振，拿下了「黃金寬帽」(意即球員在單一比賽吞下四次三振的術語)。他也是遊騎兵隊隊史最快達成此項紀錄的球員。<ref>{{cite web|last=Grant|first=Evan|title=Why Rangers aren't concerned about Joey Gallo's first 'Golden Sombrero'|website=[[The_Dallas_Morning_News|The Dallas Morning News]]|date=June 6, 2015|url=http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/2015/06/texas-rangers-manager-jeff-banister-not-conerned-after-four-strikeout-game-for-joey-gallo.html/|access-date=August 10, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809103549/http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/2015/06/texas-rangers-manager-jeff-banister-not-conerned-after-four-strikeout-game-for-joey-gallo.html/|archive-date=2015-08-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>6月30日，因為[[喬許·漢米爾頓_(運動員)|喬許·漢米爾頓]]回歸，因此蓋洛被下放到小聯盟。這年他在大聯盟的打擊率為2成04，敲出了6轟卻吞下57次三振。<ref name=autogenerated2>{{Cite web |url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=608336#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL |title=Joey Gallo Stats, Highlights, Bio {{!}} MiLB.com Stats {{!}} The Official Site of Minor League Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030153410/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=608336#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2016年====
[[File:Joey_Gallo_on_August_31,_2016.jpg|thumb]]
這年他幾乎都待在小聯盟，只在大聯盟出賽17場比賽。他僅僅25個打席就吞下19次三振，只敲出1安和1轟。<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/g/gallojo01.shtml |title=Joey Gallo Stats {{!}} Baseball-Reference.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2021-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703040815/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/g/gallojo01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2017年====
這年蓋洛成功進入開季名單，整年打擊率為2成09，並敲出41轟與80分打點。<ref name=autogenerated1 />他的飛球比(54.2%)、強勁擊球比(46.4%)和揮空率(40.9%)都是大聯盟最高。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,a |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2017 » Batters » Plate Discipline Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2018-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223163858/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,a |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2018&month=0&season1=2018&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=19,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2018 » Batters » Batted Ball Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2018-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223030032/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2018&month=0&season1=2018&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=19,d |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=7,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2017 » Batters » Batted Ball Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2018-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181222082110/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=7,d |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2018年====
這年蓋洛的打擊率只有2成06，不過他平均每12.5個打席就會開轟。他敲出40轟與92分打點，但卻擁有全大聯盟最高的揮空率(38.3%)。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2018&month=0&season1=2018&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,a |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2018 » Batters » Plate Discipline Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2018-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223163844/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2018&month=0&season1=2018&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,a |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2019年====
4月中，蓋洛拿下美聯單週最佳球員。<ref>{{cite web|author=David Adler|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/players-of-the-week-yelich-gallo|title=Yelich, Gallo power way to POTW honors|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|date=April 22, 2019|access-date=April 22, 2019|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422225857/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/players-of-the-week-yelich-gallo|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月8日，蓋洛敲出生涯第100轟。<ref name=100hr>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-hits-100th-career-homer|last=Crouse|first=Jake|title=Weird record: Gallo has 100 HRs, 93 singles|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|date=May 8, 2019|access-date=May 8, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108002339/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-hits-100th-career-homer|dead-url=no}}</ref>他以377場比賽達陣成為當時美聯史上最快達標紀錄，直到日後才被[[蓋瑞·桑契斯|蓋瑞·桑契斯]]以355場比賽超越。<ref name=100hr/>當時蓋洛的一壘安打只有93支，寫下當時大聯盟歷史新低紀錄。5月31日，蓋洛敲出生涯首支滿貫砲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dfw.cbslocal.com/2019/05/31/joey-gallo-first-career-grand-slam-rangers-royals/|title=Joey Gallo Connects For First Career Grand Slam As Rangers Defeat Royals 6-2|website=[[KTVT|CBS DFW]]|date=May 31, 2019|access-date=June 2, 2019|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202033228/https://dfw.cbslocal.com/2019/05/31/joey-gallo-first-career-grand-slam-rangers-royals/|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月25日，他因為左斜肌受傷而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-returns-from-injured-list|title=Joey Gallo back from IL, batting fifth|author=James Schmehl|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|date=June 25, 2019|access-date=June 25, 2019|archive-date=2019-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628120940/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-returns-from-injured-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他也以替補外野手身分入選明星賽，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/rangers-2019-all-stars-joey-gallo-mike-minor-hunter-pence|title=Career years earn Gallo, Minor 1st All-Star nods|author=Dawn Klemish|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|date=June 30, 2019|access-date=June 30, 2019|archive-date=2019-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924155328/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/rangers-2019-all-stars-joey-gallo-mike-minor-hunter-pence|dead-url=no}}</ref>並在他唯一一個打席中開轟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-home-run-all-star-game|title=Gallo swats record blast on first pitch he sees|author=T.R. Sullivan|website=MLB.com|date=July 9, 2019|access-date=July 10, 2019|archive-date=2019-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925104341/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-home-run-all-star-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月25日，蓋洛因為右手鉤骨受傷而動手術，使得整季報銷。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-wrist-surgery-hamate-bone|title=Gallo headed for surgery to fix hamate bone|author=T.R. Sullivan|website=MLB.com|date=July 25, 2019|access-date=July 25, 2019|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809112920/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-wrist-surgery-hamate-bone|dead-url=no}}</ref>整年他的打擊率為2成53，並敲出22轟與49分打點。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/sports/rangers/2019/09/20/joey-gallo-moved-to-60-day-il-rangers-don-t-expect-him-to-play-again-this-season/|title=Joey Gallo moved to 60-day IL, Rangers don't expect him to play again this season|author=Evan Grant|newspaper=[[The_Dallas_Morning_News|The Dallas Morning News]]|date=September 20, 2019|access-date=September 29, 2019|archive-date=2019-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929124944/https://www.dallasnews.com/sports/rangers/2019/09/20/joey-gallo-moved-to-60-day-il-rangers-don-t-expect-him-to-play-again-this-season/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====2020年====
7月6日，蓋洛確診COVID-19，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/sports/rangers/2020/07/06/rangers-rf-joey-gallo-tests-positive-for-covid-19/|title=Rangers OF Joey Gallo tests positive for COVID-19|date=July 6, 2020|first1=Sam|last1=Blum|work=[[The_Dallas_Morning_News|The Dallas Morning News]]|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2020-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214060713/https://www.dallasnews.com/sports/rangers/2020/07/06/rangers-rf-joey-gallo-tests-positive-for-covid-19/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他是名無症狀感染者。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-06|title=Asymptomatic All-Star slugger Gallo tests positive for virus|url=https://apnews.com/0e041c0f618e8a20644834e16e5af959|access-date=2020-07-07|website=AP NEWS|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205212326/https://apnews.com/0e041c0f618e8a20644834e16e5af959|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在這年的打擊率僅1成81，並敲出10轟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/g/gallojo01.shtml|title=存档副本|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703040815/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/g/gallojo01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>
另外他也獲得生涯首座金手套獎。<ref>{{Cite web|title=2020 Rawlings Gold Glove Award® Winners Announced|url=https://news.yahoo.com/2020-rawlings-gold-glove-award-020000443.html|access-date=2020-11-04|website=news.yahoo.com|language=en-US}}</ref>
====2021年====
4月9日，教士隊的[[喬·馬斯葛洛夫|喬·馬斯葛洛夫]]投出無安打比賽，而蓋洛成為遊騎兵唯一一位站上壘包的選手。這年他還入選明星賽，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-notches-two-homer-game-vs-tigers|title=902 feet?! Gallo hits 22nd, 23rd HRs of '21|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|author=Kennedi Landry|date=July 7, 2021|access-date=July 8, 2021|archive-date=2021-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210806113615/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/joey-gallo-notches-two-homer-game-vs-tigers|dead-url=no}}</ref>並參加全壘打大賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/31777964/washington-nationals-juan-soto-texas-rangers-joey-gallo-join-field-all-star-home-run-derby-coors-field|title=Washington Nationals' Juan Soto, Texas Rangers' Joey Gallo join field for All-Star Home Run Derby at Coors Field|website=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|author=ESPN News Services|date=July 8, 2021|access-date=July 8, 2021|archive-date=2021-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818185735/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/31777964/washington-nationals-juan-soto-texas-rangers-joey-gallo-join-field-all-star-home-run-derby-coors-field|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===紐約洋基===
2021年7月29日，遊騎兵將蓋洛和[[喬利·羅德里格斯|喬利·羅德里格斯]]交易到洋基，換來Josh Smith、Glenn Otto、Trevor Hauver和Ezequiel Duran。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/YankeesPR/status/1420776156148768780 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-07-29 |archive-date=2021-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825032531/https://twitter.com/YankeesPR/status/1420776156148768780 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==個人生活==
蓋洛小時候在拉斯維加斯長大，[[布萊斯·哈波|布萊斯·哈波]]和[[克里斯·布萊恩|克里斯·布萊恩]]都曾是蓋洛小時候加入的棒球隊隊友。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportsday.dallasnews.com/texas-rangers/rangers/2018/04/17/joey-gallos-career-catcher-ended-young-bryce-harper-made-cry|title=Joey Gallo's career as a catcher ended because a young Bryce Harper once made him cry|author=Joey Hayden|website=[[The_Dallas_Morning_News|The Dallas Morning News]]|date=April 17, 2018|access-date=June 2, 2019|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602150623/https://sportsday.dallasnews.com/texas-rangers/rangers/2018/04/17/joey-gallos-career-catcher-ended-young-bryce-harper-made-cry|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=BG/>布萊恩的父親麥克也曾指導過蓋洛棒球，<ref name=BG>{{cite web|url=https://www.milb.com/pacific-coast/news/rise-to-top-a-family-affair-for-bryant-gallo/c-116978986|title=Rise to top a family affair for Bryant, Gallo|publisher=MiLB.com|author=Tyler Maun|date=April 9, 2015|access-date=June 2, 2019|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602150622/https://www.milb.com/pacific-coast/news/rise-to-top-a-family-affair-for-bryant-gallo/c-116978986|dead-url=no}}</ref>而蓋洛的父親湯尼曾在1974年打過小聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=gallo-002ant|title=Anthony Gallo|website=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=June 2, 2019}}</ref><ref name=BG/>

2020年，大聯盟因為COVID-19疫情而延後開季。蓋洛便在這段期間於自家設立簡易打擊鳥籠維持打擊手感。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dallasnews.com/sports/rangers/2020/03/29/im-sorry-neighbors-rangers-joey-gallo-turns-home-into-indoor-batting-cage-during-coronavirus-quarantine/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125083231/https://www.dallasnews.com/sports/rangers/2020/03/29/im-sorry-neighbors-rangers-joey-gallo-turns-home-into-indoor-batting-cage-during-coronavirus-quarantine/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
